### [5] POST record vitals - as MANAGER
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/vitalsign/recordvital
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: MANAGER

{
  "taskId": 6,
  "residentId": 5,
  "bloodPressureSystolic": 125,
  "bloodPressureDiastolic": 82,
  "heartRateBpm": 80,
  "spo2Percentage": 97,
  "temperatureFahrenheit": 98.9,
  "respiratoryRate": 17,
  "painScale": 3,
  "notes": "Routine morning vitals"
}

