### [6] FORBIDDEN - wrong role (DON cannot record vitals)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/vitalsign/recordvital
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: DON

{
  "taskId": 1,
  "residentId": 1,
  "bloodPressureSystolic": 120,
